data.description: Enjoy Country living within the city! Relax under the fully covered front porch (9x27') and a white picked front yard. The front yard is shaded by mature trees which aids in keeping the house cool in the summer. The home was remodled in 2021.  Walk into your home and you'll see the newly remodeled kitchen with quartz counter tops, high end cabinetry, and new appliances. The range top is an induction surface. The barn door pantry is huge! There are four Senville AURA Series Mini Split Air Conditioner/Inverter Heat Pumps. Check out the newly created master bathroom with walkin closet and partially remolded guest bathroom. Enjoy mountain views from the dining room table. A huge plus are the 50 year architecture shingles, majority of the windows have been replaced and updated. New flooring throughout 90% of the home, and new siding installed around the entire home along with R-13 Value insulation board to keep you warm in the winter and cool in the summers. The SOLAR SYSTEM cost is  $138/ Month and Buyer must assume.  Which basically gives you a zero cost for electricity PLUS the electric credits. There is FREE internet through Elite Broadband (Tower on Property). There is endless use of the oversized two car garage and expansive heated shop (35 X 60) which can easily fit an RV and your toys. They is an enclosed room which has many possibilities.  The horse corral structure is ready for your final designs. If you want space and privacy this is for you! No HOA and/or covenants.  Come check out this lovely home and unique property.
